                 ],
                 "paragraph-body":[
                    {
                       "type":"paragraph",
                       "text":"Luxo Italia",
                       "spans":[
                          
                       ]
                    },
                    {
                       "type":"paragraph",
                       "text":"Since we’re always on the lookout for the next best thing in Italian luxury travel, the Luxo Italia Instagram is a failsafe source of inspiration when planning your next trip to Italy. If you aren’t already following us, we recommend taking a look!",
                       "spans":[
                          
